And - cook - cook general, into - into a public house quite adjacent to - a busy public house quite adjacent to the wharves and the docks. My family were always the - that was the first introduction to the public house life and my eldest brother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6173087 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8660755\charrsid5717858 That would be 1913 when you did that?
