Well - same as any other child, we always had to work hard, we had to work hard for our - our living, I mean - it was expected as a youngster any money you earned you brought into the h
ome. And - in repayment for - the years when - they had to look after you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6173087 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8660755\charrsid5717858 Did she bring you up to consider certain things important in life?
