Oh yes, she was very on the - church side. Oh very strict on that. That - that we attended - bible class, the Sunday morning church and bible class, evening as well, that was up to - up to us but - then we become naturally under the control of the vicar.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6173087 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8660755\charrsid5717858 Did you ever go on any choir outings?
