\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4592392\charrsid5717858 priest}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8660755\charrsid5717858  would be round searching 'em out, wanting to know why. They were
 more 'course the - Catholics were more devout to that sort of thing, but - gradually as they got older it peeled off a bit. But - it - it - as churchgoers in the {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}East End{\*\xmlclose}
 they were - the Catholic community - and - and the Jewish community were the more devout - out of the lot.
