s, I went hopping once, with - with - with some friends of mother, but mother - mother was a regular hopper, as a young girl. She always went - always - always - she said to me, you'd better go hopping now, you're getting a - and see it for yourself, beca
use that's where you used to spend your holidays when you was a kid. In a bath, down hopping while, she said, we was out in the hop fields earning a few bob.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6173087 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8660755\charrsid5717858 Can you remember that?
