r went, well because who were you meeting, you was meeting the same people. No, I - as a young man I had me bike. I - all my pleasure was on me bike and - and to evade the traffic of the day - if we ever - if we ever went to Southend we used to - night ri
de. Start off about nine o'clock - and then -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6173087 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8660755\charrsid5717858 Was this after you left school or before?
